{"tid":1470400,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"阻入上機唔岩？入嚟聽我講兩句","createTime":"2019-08-14T05:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T05:44:41.000Z","uid":9906,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1b0f444c216f07f553d2669e8a0bda73a35dd2cf","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:13:57.000Z","msg":"見到881又屌，連登有一派又屌，首先要指出嘅係，尋日最大嘅問題源於&mdash;&mdash;<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">未有共識</div></span></span><br />\n<br />\n去機場嘅各位手足麻煩問一問自己，意義係乜？只係單單想向旅客宣傳，定還是想癱瘓機場？搞清楚先，要玩落去，機場嘅各位首先要抱著同樣嘅前提。<br />\n<br />\n如果大家嘅共識係癱瘓機場，咁阻旅客上機，正正就係用緊和理非手段逼政府對話。<span style=\"color: red;\">如果唔咁做，機場又可以正常運作，等同影響力有限，變返夏慤村模式。</span><br />\n<br />\n有人或者會擔心外國旅客觀感，但<span style=\"color: red;\">外國旅客點睇重要咩？佢地觀感對成場運動有幾大影響？</span>你阻佢實會怪罪你，但只要機場繼續保持和理非，被國際睇到晒，咁先可以爭取國際支持，先係運動關鍵。<span style=\"color: red;\">亦只有和理非，先吸到淺黃/中間/潔癖人士。</span><br />\n<br />\n至於受影響旅客，你可以選擇行多步，好似尋日有巴打幫佢地揾交通揾酒店⋯⋯呢啲係可以做，但絕對唔可以因為阻到旅客就話要割蓆！<br />\n<br />\n另外，<span style=\"color: red;\">屌阻上機嘅人有無諗過，如何係唔搞到人嘅情況下癱瘓機場？</span>有嘅麻煩提出，但我諗極都係覺得，無！塞爆其實都係會影響佢地，不論主動被動，再多幾日佢地都好難再體諒，最後都係怪返示威者。<br />\n<br />\n機場係終極牌，如果無法癱瘓機場，政府繼續wfc，場運動無可能會成功。<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔應該阻人上機」呢種諗法已經被政府利用，利用呢種心態譴責示威者，製造輿論製造分化。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總結尋晚做得未夠好嘅位：<br />\n<br />\n一、勇武派同警方起衝突，令佢地有理由申請到禁令。<br />\n<br />\n二、未有共識，以至癱瘓機場行動失敗，出現分裂跡象，爆眼少女嘅輿論被轉移<br />\n<br />\n三、綁手綁腳同打人呢啲唔夠和理非，失咗班潔僻撚嘅支持（好on9但係現實）<br />\n<br />\n捉鬼係應該要做，但阻警車、搶警棍、綁手腳呢啲做多咗，雖然報到仇係爽，<span style=\"color: red;\">但如果為咗報一時之快代價係逐漸失去支持者，長遠嚟講都係輸，終極報仇（清算警察）都係遙遙無期。</span><br />\n<br />\n建議對應方法如下：<br />\n<br />\n一、停止同警察再衝突，法庭已出禁令，但仍允許和平示威，麻煩大家珍惜最後機會。<br />\n<br />\n二、達成阻旅客上機共識，將輿論spin到「阻人上機能夠符合公義。<br />\n<br />\n三、建立規矩，只准和理非，綁手綁腳同打人都可免則免啦。知道大家好想報仇，但請忍忍手，如果唔係好難捉到鬼。<br />\n<br />\n以上係咁多，諗到再加"},{"pid":"5e689986c0870014e3bbd345b5c243107f03e970","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:15:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cd6d5701dbf8c21c204d852c6c6eb8c963dfd1a1","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:16:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"dbc4e40b5dbc232c15811168d05255ab00f700ed","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:18:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"234b99295f4e86b2e32fb1686d45fb91304f1fd0","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:18:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3b365292941f96dd6117d9366c353091792d2aa3","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f06e9173d53887ba2a87cb6103e5e487dde39ac","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:18:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4a9ab1de05947598d71d20b1c54054b612be92d","tid":1470400,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:18:52.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"afbce949478ada1331a0333ca9e34e1e207b4bd3","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:19:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4b74cb00c02835b64dd068f77b2d6481a7cdc27b","tid":1470400,"uid":32719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:19:16.000Z","msg":"(突發)航空公司   民航處  機管局講大話<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468306\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468306</a><br />\n<br />\n所有政府部門都係蛇鼠一窩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要求政府 機管局 民航處 交待事件"},{"pid":"c9d8eb5e73c2bdb437985ab8bf8b3f5895d52e06","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:20:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"12bec1bf77b196bfca2227b52aad9ebb72f40cf4","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:22:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"07ce23589901d56e8bb71f38ae0be4ba2a5fc643","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:24:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cbdd53006edfacf68aff798cf48af2f978b2c66b","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:24:17.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6ad16b9d9bcd86a6a1d8aaff93d382b9a9684df9","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:24:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5a24bec8d581ef4d2666c9abbb24142ee655644d","tid":1470400,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:26:07.000Z","msg":"從來都唔係【癱唔癱】既問題，而係【如何癱】既問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dDEQpS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dDEQpS</a>"},{"pid":"eabbf8ab1fa3607d9b85a74d1b6e85f5affdacfc","tid":1470400,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:27:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d59984afff0a7ebcff84fb60488f37725c1568e","tid":1470400,"uid":259284,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"次次一有威脅到政權嘅活動出現，<br />\n就有民意燃衝出黎大叫，停手呀，失民意啦失民意啦，<br />\n都唔知係五毛定真心膠，<br />\n民意燃真心覺得有抗爭方式係有效得黎，<br />\n而又乜人都影響唔到?<br />\n遊行靜坐都會阻路俾人屌架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係話民意完全無用，<br />\n但香港又唔係民主政府，幾時聽過民意，<br />\n民意燃仲想攬住民意過世? <br />\n文宣到有700萬人一齊遊行，政權就會屈服?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n文宣到全世界強烈譴責，佢地就會出兵幫手打政府? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無人救過死左好多人嘅烏克蘭、蘇丹、新疆?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n自己香港要靠自己救，唔係齋有民意就得，<br />\n任何威脅到政權嘅方法都要試，<br />\n唔好本末倒置，因為民意勒索而乜都唔敢做，<br />\n各有各做，出核彈都唔割"},{"pid":"56fb8e817bf9cb9280fb655827b13aee4f0dd8c2","tid":1470400,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:44:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n［高手請入］在情在理，唔需要道歉，只需要國際級文宣洗白<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470244\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470244</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}